Ignore the following cases

- `array<int, TypeName>`
- `array{'key': TypeName}`

#### Example

```php
<?php
namespace Test1;

class Foo {
    
}

namespace Test2;

class Test
{
    /**
     * @param array<'foo', Foo> $param
     */
    public function test1(array $param): Foo {
        return $param['foo'];
    }

    /**
     * @param array{'foo': Foo, "bar": string} $param
     */
    public function test2(array $param): Foo {
        return $param['foo'];
    }
}

```

